<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IFrameBufferOutput.GetImageDimensions" Title="GetImageDimensions method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IFrameBufferOutput">IFrameBufferOutput</PageRef> ->
    GetImageDimensions
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetImageDimensions</TypeRef> method returns the size in pixels of the image data in the output buffer.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[V2UInt32 GetImageDimensions() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="V2UInt32">
        The dimensions of the captured framebuffer image, in pixels.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
